[thinking] **Figuring out method reflection**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about the native reflection for getMethods and whether it requires queryAllPublicMethods or just methods. In the native implementation, the method invoke seems to need invoke metadata. Since the config for "methods" allows for both invoke and query, that makes me wonder if the native image reflection config “methods” is indeed what makes both executable and queryable. There’s quite a lot here to unpack!
[thinking] 
